                "control-id": "hipaa-sec164-312b",
                "description": "Splunk use case UC-22.35.1 provides full assurance in mode 'satisfies' for HIPAA 2013-final clause \u00a7164.312(b). Rationale: \u00a7164.312(b) 'Audit controls' is satisfied when the covered entity can show audit logs are captured continuously; this UC produces that evidence directly.",
