                "description": "Splunk use case UC-22.35.1 provides contributing assurance in mode 'detects-violation-of' for SOX-ITGC PCAOB AS 2201 clause ITGC.Logging.Continuity. Rationale: A material weakness finding for ITGCs often follows from unexplained gaps in the audit trail; this UC raises the signal but SOX evidence requires additional management attestation.",
